title: Bug 114470[Smoke]Error message throws when using new Date("3/2/2005") as value in table filter.
OB: Error message is thrown when attempting to use the value 'new Date("3/2/2005")' in a table filter.
EB: The error message should not be thrown when using 'new Date("3/2/2005")' as a value in the table filter.
SR:
The issue can be reproduced by following these steps:
1. Open the table filter.
2. Enter the value 'new Date("3/2/2005")' in the filter.
3. Observe the error message being thrown.
